<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Verification - Email Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Dear <%=display_name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for creating an account with our service! To activate your account and start using our platform,
            please click on the following link:</p>
        <p><a href="<%=verify_account_url %>" class="btn">Verify Your Account</a></p>
        <p>If you didn't create an account with us, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The <%=project_name %> Team</p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>